content: ​Traveloka sangat cocok untuk Anda yang mencari kemudahan dan kelengkapan dalam merencanakan perjalanan. Jika Anda menghargai berbagai pilihan, harga yang kompetitif, dan antarmuka yang ramah pengguna, platform ini bisa menjadi pilihan yang sangat baik. Namun, penting untuk selalu membaca syarat dan ketentuan dengan teliti, terutama untuk kebijakan pembatalan dan perubahan jadwal.
content_en: Traveloka is perfect for those of you who are looking for ease and completeness in planning a trip. If you value a wide range of options, competitive prices, and a user-friendly interface, this platform can be an excellent choice. However, it is important to always read the terms and conditions carefully, especially for cancellation and schedule change policies.

content: Lumayan responsif call center nya.. Proses penanganannya juga lumayan cepat dan mudah. Aku reschedule jadwal penerbangan tiket pesawat, prosesnya cuma sejam. Tapi polis asuransi aku tanggalnya gak berubah, jadi aku chat call centernya. Gercep dan responsif banget, aku chat jam 9 malam, jam 2 pagi udah dikirimi polis yg baru sesuai tanggal. Padahal berangkatnya udah mepet banget, jam 6 pagi. Walaupun perusahaan asuransi nya beda perusahaan sama Traveloka nya, tapi prosesnya tergolong cepat.
content_en: The call center is quite responsive... The handling process is also quite fast and easy. I rescheduled my flight ticket, the process took only an hour. But my insurance policy date didn't change, so I chatted with the call center. Very fast and responsive, I chat at 9 pm, at 2 am I was already sent a new policy according to the date. Even though the departure was very tight, at 6 am. Although the insurance company is a different company from Traveloka, the process is relatively fast.

content: Udah jadi penikmat aplikasi ini sejak lama.Baru kali ini merasa dirugikan karena sistemnya mengubah tgl booking. Saat komplain ke IG traveloka.id infonya sedang ada lonjakan pelaporan.Booking room buat tgl 5 sept, sudah sampai preview data masih tertulis data yg sama. saat pembayaran & dikirim e-ticket kenapa tgl berubah jadi tgl 10 sept? sudah konfirmasi ke pihak akomodasi, alesannya semua room sudah penuh karena memang moment long weekend. tidak bisa refund & reschedule, customer jadi KORBAN.
content_en: I've been a fan of this application for a long time. This is the first time I feel aggrieved because the system changes the booking date. When complaining to IG traveloka.id, the information is that there is a surge in reporting. Booking a room for September 5, already until the preview data is still written the same data. when paying & sending e-tickets why did the date change to September 10? already confirmed to the accommodation, the reason is that all rooms are full because it is a long weekend moment. cannot refund & reschedule, the customer becomes a victim.

content: Pada 16 Agustus 2025 pukul 11.42, TPayLater saya mendapat kenaikan level ke level 6. Namun hanya berselang tiga hari pada 19 Agustus 2025 level saya tiba-tiba diturunkan menjadi level 3. Hal ini membuat saya bingung dan kecewa, karena saya tidak melakukan pelanggaran. Tidak ada notifikasi maupun penjelasan yang jelas terkait penurunan level ini. Sebagai pengguna setia, saya berharap pihak Traveloka dapat memberikan klarifikasi dan transparansi mengenai penyebab perubahan level yang begitu cepat.
content_en: On August 16, 2025 at 11:42 am, my TPayLater got a level up to level 6. But only three days later on August 19, 2025 my level was suddenly lowered to level 3. This left me confused and disappointed, as I had not committed any violations. There is no notification or clear explanation regarding this level drop. As a loyal user, I hope Traveloka can provide clarification and transparency regarding the cause of such a rapid level change.

content: Tadinya Saya pengguna setia TPayLater yg sdh mencapai level 6 dan tidak pernah telat bayar tagihan tiap bulan nya. Tapi entah alasan yg tidak jelas, kemarin setelah saya bayar tagihan saya, LEVEL SAYA MALAH DITURUNKAN DAN SAYA TIDAK BISA PAKAI LAGI TPAYLATER NYA Karena alasan sdh melebihi limit pemakaian setelah diturunkan level limit nya ke level2. Ini terkesan menjebak pengguna paylater mencapai limit dan membayar sisa limit tagihan teringgi sebelumnya. Semoga dibaca pengguna lain dan YLKI.
content_en: I used to be a loyal TPayLater user who has reached level 6 and has never been late paying bills every month. But for some unclear reason, yesterday after I paid my bill, MY LEVEL WAS REDUCED AND I CANNOT USE THE TPAYLATER AGAIN for the reason that I have exceeded the usage limit after lowering the limit level to level2. This seems to trap paylater users to reach the limit and pay the remaining limit of the previous highest bill. Hopefully other users and YLKI will read it.

content: Berguna kalo hari biasa. Kalo liburan tiba, mendadak jadi KARTEL hotel. Kamar langsung pada kosong dan harga naik 5x lipat lebih hanya dlm hitungan detik. Parahnya aplikasi serupa sama sprti itu ibarat sudah diatur Sistem KATTELISASI. Alhasil kalo pas liburan saran saya pakai tiktok atau IG cari villa dengan promo menarik atau le3at kenalan sanak sodara dan teman di tujuan liburan.
content_en: Useful on weekdays. When the holidays come, it suddenly becomes a hotel CARTEL. Rooms are immediately empty and prices increase 5x more in just a matter of seconds. The worst thing is that similar applications are like a CATTELIZATION system. As a result, when on vacation, my advice is to use tiktok or IG to look for villas with attractive promos or le3at acquaintances of relatives and friends at vacation destinations.

content: Hati2 jebakan batman,,saat semua hotel full book...aplikasi ini akan menawarkan dgn kesediaan tgl dan harga yg suitable seolah2..bagi yg tdk teliti akan menganggap itu sesuai,,padahal saat hotel full book pada tgl tsb, aplikasi mengganti bulan'a dibulan depan dgn memakai tgl yg sama..sehingga kita melakukan transaksi dgn ketentuan no refund & no reschedule...saat ke hotel baru disadari ternyata tgl yg sama tapi utk bulan depan...hati2 dan waspada.
content_en: Be careful of batman traps, when all hotels are fully booked ... this application will offer with the availability of suitable dates and prices as if ... for those who are not careful will assume it is appropriate, even though when the hotel is fully booked on that date, the application replaces the month'a next month by using the same date... so that we make transactions with the provisions of no refund & no reschedule ... when we go to the hotel we realize that it turns out to be the same date but for next month ... be careful and alert.

Finally the extra bed was all included and we moved to a bigger room. Amazing Traveloka! good luck!

Masuk akal ngk klo penerbangan yg dibatalkan maskapai, dr harga 9,2jt. yg direfund cuma 8,5jt. padahal pihak maskapai lohhh yg batalin penerbangan. jd bukan salah dr kita. tp customer yg dirugikan.
content_en: Goodbye Traveloka. It's been 10 years even though I subscribed to km. I'm even a Platinum member. But you are really disappointing. The phone of the operator's person is now gone. instead, everything is diverted to the robot operator. so we are forced to accept the results of traveloka without being able to ask clear questions. It makes sense if the flight canceled by the airline, from the price of 9.2 million. which was refunded only 8.5 million. even though the airline canceled the flight. so it's not our fault. but the customer is harmed.

content: Sangat mengecewakan! Aplikasi sebesar Traveloka, seperti toko sebelah, memasarkan penginapan murah. Setelah memesan dan tiba saat check-in, kami ditolak pihak hotel. Kasus pertama: harga tidak sesuai aplikasi. Kasus kedua: akomodasi tidak bekerja sama dengan Traveloka. Ini sangat menjebak pelanggan yang sudah datang jauh-jauh, lalu ditolak. Mencari penginapan di hari yang sama seringkali jauh lebih mahal untuk akomodasi sejenis. Hati-hati! Anda berjudi dengan reputasi Traveloka yang sudah bagus.
content_en: Very disappointing! An app as big as Traveloka, like the shop next door, markets cheap lodging. After booking and arriving at check-in, we were rejected by the hotel. First case: the price does not match the application. Second case: the accommodation does not cooperate with Traveloka. This is very tricky for customers who have come all the way, then get rejected. Finding lodging on the same day is often much more expensive for similar accommodations. Beware! You are gambling with Traveloka's good reputation.

content: Liburan ke Jepang kemarin bener-bener nggak ribet karena semua aku pesen lewat Traveloka—mulai dari tiket pesawat, hotel, sampai tiket masuk ke beberapa tempat wisata kayak Universal Studios Japan dan TeamLab. Proses booking-nya cepet, info lengkap, dan bisa langsung dapet e-voucher, jadi tinggal tunjukin pas sampai lokasi. Aku juga suka banget fitur notifikasi dari Traveloka yang ngingetin jadwal dan ngasih update penting. Semua serba praktis dan nyaman, bikin liburannya jadi lebih tenang
content_en: My vacation to Japan yesterday was really hassle-free because I booked everything through Traveloka-from flight tickets, hotels, to entrance tickets to several tourist attractions such as Universal Studios Japan and TeamLab. The booking process was fast, the information was complete, and you can immediately get an e-voucher, so you just need to show it when you arrive at the location. I also really like the notification feature from Traveloka that reminds me of my schedule and gives me important updates. Everything is practical and convenient, making the vacation more peaceful.

content: Hati2 menggunakan traveloka karena sistem pembayaran kurang aman tanpa adanya menggunakan otp saat transaksi. Sehingga CC kalau dipegang orang lain dapat dilakukan transaksi tanpa harus konfirmasi validasi. Itu sebuah kelemahan. Saya sangat dirugikan oleh traveloka dan saya harus membayar 6 tiket pesawat hanya utk 2 orang penumpang yang sama akibat sistemnya eror, mutar2 blank. Dan tidak diketahui kalau sudah terbeli. Saya kecewa akan hal tersebut. Hati2 menggunkana traveloka. Terima kasih.
content_en: Be careful using traveloka because the payment system is less secure without using otp during transactions. So that if the CC is held by someone else, transactions can be made without having to confirm validation. That is a weakness. I was very disadvantaged by traveloka and I had to pay for 6 airplane tickets only for the same 2 passengers due to the system error, turning blank. And it is not known if it has been purchased. I was disappointed with that. Be careful using traveloka. Thank you.

content: 1. Reschedule dilakukan maskapai pada penerbangan transit di H-1, pembeli mau refund kena potongan sekitar 250ribuan/org. Padahal kesalahan maskapai, tapi potongan refund sebesar itu. content_en: 1. Reschedule done by the airline on a transit flight on H-1, the buyer wants to refund a deduction of about 250 thousand / person. Even though it's the airline's fault, but the refund deduction is that big. Not to mention the time-consuming disbursement. 2. Because of the transit flight. The first flight was rescheduled, delayed before the second flight was due. Wanted to ask the CS, what is the solution. Eh, the CS is a robot. When I wanted to go to the helpdesk, I waited for a long time without replying to the message. Kapoklah use Traveloka if this is the model.

Sure enough from the schedule at 17:30 it can only fly at 19:00 Based on the clause from chubb that when there is a minimum delay of 90 minutes, the insurance can be claimed, it has been claimed but there is no settlement yet.... Traveloka & chubb lie
